Want to be able to hot swap a class after, say, method addition/removal?
This is a plugin for you then! This is an IntelliJ IDEA plugin which
provides integration with [DCEVM][] - an OpenJDK-based JVM which fixes
standard [java HotSwap][].

  [DCEVM]: http://ssw.jku.at/dcevm/
  [java HotSwap]: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hot_swapping